  "title": "Project Engineer (East) - #HHW",
  "description": "<p>Job Scope:</p><ul><li>Manage and coordinate project works as assigned by lead engineer and project manager.</li><li>Coordinate with management, team members, vendors, contractors, and client representatives.</li><li>Update and report to management team.</li><li>Assist and support the site supervisor and construction manager in all aspects of works, including:</li><li>Planning and scheduling work</li><li>Assigning work to sub-contractors and overseeing their work.</li><li>Ensuring compliance with standards, codes, and safety regulations.</li><li>Developing reports and records</li><li>Maintaining accurate records and documentation.</li></ul><p></p><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min. Diploma in any field and above.</li><li>Possess class 3 driving license and own a car (required to travel to various site locations for work).</li><li>Min 3 years experience as Project Manager </li><li>Prior experience from contruction industry is an added advantage</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested candidates, please send your resume to <a href=\"mailto:jonathanlim@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">wendykhoo@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Wendy Khoo Hui Wen<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd <br />EA Licence No: 99C4599<br />CEI Registration Number: R1761665</p>",
